- EH&S Monthly Report 2025-01
January 2025. Story Highlights: Hamilton Hall flooding, new shared accountability process for lab safety issues - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-02
February 2025. Story Highlights: Bat incidence response plan with DOR, new forklift operator safety training process - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-03
March 2025. Story Highlights: Respirator certification for bird flu researchers, gas decontamination of BSL3 labs - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-04
April 2025: Story Highlights: Laser inspection for FFA conference, touring waste management contractor's facilities - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-05
May 2025. Story Highlights: Reiman Gardens firefighter walkthroughs, lead abatement started for Wilson Hall - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-06
June 2025. Story Highlights: Lab Safety Workshop attendance recognition, ISU Dairy Farm fire investigation - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-07
July 2025. Story Highlights: Phase one of the lead abatement project in Wilson Hall has been completed, safety training courses updated in Canvas - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-08
August 2025. Story Highlights: Emergency Medical Cabinet training for Vet Med, peroxide-forming chemical training for the Nanovaccine Institute - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-09
September 2025: Story highlights: EOC activation for Cy-Hawk game, Campus Fire Safety Day, drone incident. - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-10
October 2025. Story highlights: RMF tours, fire safety during homecoming, Beardshear roof replacement. - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-11
November 2025. Story Highlights: Intramural champions, Dairy Farm fire, campus safety walk. - EH&S Monthly Report 2025-12
December 2025. Story Highlights: Agronomy laboratory fire, Chemical Inventory launch, mercury release response. - EH&S Monthly Report 2026-01
January 2026. Story Highlights: Laboratory cleanout, Mercury release follow-up, Lithium battery waste - EH&S Monthly Report 2026-02
Februrary 2026. Story Highlights: Lab Safety Week, Formaldehyde monitoring, Radiation exposure response - EHS Annual Report 2024
